cross: Paphiopedilum Hsinying Citron x Paphiopedilum Alma Gevaert
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: One large, full, flat flower on one tall 31-cm erect inflorescence; sepals white, bold green striping; petals white, intense concentrated green striping and a few spots; pouch lime green; staminode lime green, intense emerald markings centrally; substance firm; texture matte.
